name: A count thing
description: A choreography of people doing numbers from 1 to 10. Using the condemned Flash animation software. When rendering it to a video file, some unwanted artefacts appeared. Someday the software and the hardware will stop working. Until then I keep on dancing and counting. 2020 CR 930 https://hansup.be/2020_acountthing_animation_hans-verhaegen.html
